{
  "texts": [
    "Within the context of language models and their role in shaping communication, it is imperative to remember that the values conveyed by language are fundamental in guiding human behavior and action (Habermas, 1990).",
    "Thus, the implicit values that exist within a language model may be transmitted through its use.",
    "Recent empirical research has demonstrated that the values that are embedded in the GPT-3 training data are predominantly refective of American values, rather than those of other cultural contexts (Johnson et al., 2022).",
    "Regardless, it still will be diffcult to tame this titan under these AGI conditions of \"general-purpose.\"",
    "In this case, the limits are not only ethical but also technical."
  ]
}